	.container
		h2.call_to_action__title.call_to_action__title--01
			| Become first
		span.call_to_action__text.call_to_action__text--01
			| Discover classic and brand new styles in a variety of shapes, colours and materials, from signature Frame to the latest teardrop inspired watches.

		form#mc-embedded-subscribe-form.call_to_action__form.validate.js-subscribe-form(action='//ui-market.us13.list-manage.com/subscribe/post-json?u=c753049c0b6c0ccd061d10786&id=e574a9d387&c=?', method='post', name='mc-embedded-subscribe-form', novalidate='')
			#mc_embed_signup_scroll
				.call_to_action__input_box--01
					.mc-field-group
						input#mce-EMAIL.input.input.input--dark.call_to_action__input--01.email(type='email', required, placeholder='Your email', value='', name='EMAIL')
